= Methodology
<sec:methodology>
As discussed in Section~@sec:methodology, our approach leverages deep
reinforcement learning#footnote[Specifically, Proximal Policy
Optimization (PPO).] to align outputs with human preferences.

== Data Processing
<data-processing>
The corpus is tokenized using `Byte-Pair Encoding` (BPE) with a
vocabulary size of 50,257.

